{"type":"text","timestamp":1775858190276,"sessionID":"ses_2869b1292ffeX5MBiTkvixzRwt","part":{"id":"prt_d79656dc0001sYE8d2cDWpIbth","messageID":"msg_d79656287001GdIM8STTg7i9SG","sessionID":"ses_2869b1292ffeX5MBiTkvixzRwt","type":"text","text":"## AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 — Archive Summary\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n**Core Implementation (Phase 1-3):**\n- `valkeyStore` struct with all required fields\n- `makeValkeyOptions()` — environment variable parsing (VALKEY_ADDR, VALKEY_PASSWORD, VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED, VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE, VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE)\n- `NewValkeyStore()` — client initialization\n- All Store interface methods:\n  - `Ping()`, `GetSandboxBySessionID()`, `StoreSandbox()`, `UpdateSandbox()`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()`\n  - `ListExpiredSandboxes()`, `ListInactiveSandboxes()`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity()`, `Close()`\n\n**Helper Functions (Phase 4):**\n- `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs()` with MGET batch retrieval and orphan handling\n\n**Testing (Phase 5):**\n- Unit tests: `store_valkey_test.go` (125 lines) — configuration tests for `makeValkeyOptions()`\n- Integration tests: `store_valkey_integration_test.go` (561 lines) — full functional test coverage using miniredis mock\n\n**Singleton Integration:**\n- `singleton.go` updated to support `STORE_TYPE=valkey` (case-insensitive)\n\n**Documentation (Phase 6):**\n- `doc.go` — comprehensive package documentation including key patterns, backends, singleton usage, configuration, and error handling\n\n---\n\n### ⏭️ Deferred\n\n- **Formal acceptance checklist** — tasks.md remains unchecked (tracking artifact only)\n- **Code coverage verification** — no explicit coverage report generated\n- **Integration test execution** — tests written but require actual Valkey instance to run","time":{"start":1775858190273,"end":1775858190273}}}
